WWW-ConfixxBackup
=================

This module aims to simplify making backups of Websites using Confixx.
Sometimes it is forgotten to make backups.

This module can handle either the same login data for Confixx and FTP or
different login data.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  WWW::Mechanize
  Net::FTP

